{"word":"G3573 - νυστάζω - nystázō - noos-tad'-zo - Slumber","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νυστάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">nystázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">noos-tad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Slumber</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அசட்டைப் பண்ணு. உறங்கு"},{"paragraph":"1. to nod in sleep, to sleep"},{"paragraph":"2. to be negligent, careless"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G3506 - νεύω - neúō - nyoo'-o/3506\">G3506</a>; to <i>nod</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>fall asleep</i>; figuratively to <i>delay:</i> - slumber.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}